<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bud2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bud,</orth> vb., to put forth buds or gems: <bibl n="shak. ven 1142" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 1142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. luc 604" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 604</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 95.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 95, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. pp 171" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 171</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.5.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 5, 37</bibl> <cit><quote>(young --ing virgin).</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.72" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 4, 72</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>which is --ed out,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.94" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 94</bibl></cit> (== has come to light).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>